description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Run, jump & wall kick your way through a procedurally generated world infested with dangerous insects. Chaotic platformer action. Great fun with a friend or two or three.
